{"tid":314128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"LEGO第二間認證店開張！Fans掃阿波羅火箭","createTime":"2017-07-09T02:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T02:39:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c64ddba2d92339b5c444fa12148ce72f6b168fa","tid":314128,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083952&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083952%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&d=9K4m331hoOOF5Vr9VFkABQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=ac420cf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083952%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&h=13ce6d02\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083952&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709</a><br />\n<br />\nLEGO第二間認證店開張！<br />\nFans掃阿波羅火箭<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n第二間香港認證LEGO Store昨日在銅鑼灣時代廣場開幕，逾50人一早排隊等候入場。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣LEGO Store是繼旺角朗豪坊店後全港第二間LEGO認證專門店，新店佔地逾4,000呎，繼續賣本土情懷，大展櫃放有由LEGO砌成的已拆卸羅素街電車廠場景，門外則有地道美食馬賽克磚牆。店內更設有本地首張數碼Play Table及3D minifigure合照區，加強互動性。專門店門口還有一座2米高的星戰黑武士，氣勢十足儼如「保安」。<br />\n<br />\n開張日首300名買滿300元的客人，將可獲限量版迷你電車一份；周六及周日於店內可免費索取LEGO海報一張。另外在新張期間，顧客在店內分別買滿1,500元、1,200元或800元，可獲贈樂高專門店Boxset、香港獨家尖沙嘴鐘樓或3合1迷你錢罌，但優惠不能同時使用，全部送完即止。"},{"pid":"1746181227107dd5f1f5d56a3c2a592980548c87","tid":314128,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:14:23.000Z","msg":"估唔到呢個年代都仲咁多人玩lego"},{"pid":"10fd8370babb3c09d5e9ef883d6e90ed527ce229","tid":314128,"uid":25278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到呢個年代都仲咁多人玩lego</blockquote><br />\n炒"},{"pid":"ae32642f10a9